In summary, by following the sequence $I_{B} \rightarrow I_{C} \rightarrow V_{C E}$, we have determined the key terminal currents and voltages of $Q_{1}$. Although not particularly noteworthy here, the emitter current is simply $I_{C} + I_{B}$.

